task.summary: Default task
Fixed a bunch of nav drawer issues, as well as updating code a bit. Added shells of fragments and activities that I will work on in a separate feat branch.
Added in functionality for activities and fragments to be accessed, added in preliminary views for fragments and activities.
Added more UI elements to my trips fragment
Updated My Trips fragment, and started in on My Vehicle
Updated Emergency UI, and added a login screen. Updated overflow menu. Added connection OBD UI shell stuff.
Updated UI for OBD slightly, added spot for OBD Connect in Nav drawer
Added Google + authentication ability, need to send intent with user information.
Made nav bar show result of G+ sign in.
You can now sign out... I mean... If that is something you wanna do...
New branch FEAT-AW-02
Merged CP-02 and develop
***Base new branches off of this*** Added icons for nav drawer. Updated login with loading animations.
Created ViewPager for DriveToWIn Activity. Similarly needs to be done for vechicle/insurance info.
Got rid of app loading two apks on to device.
Added stats view, and fixed issues with ViewPager not updating navDrawer
Added default user profile picture.
Added default user profile picture.
Added sign up and sign in by username and password
Merged with CP-03
Added insurance info views. Made changes for login to make UX smoother
Updated error checking, and made sign in, sign up, and sign out a smoother experience.
Fixed bug where signing out with non-gplus users would still bypass the login screen on application restart.
